00:40:35.520 --> 00:40:36.600 align:middle line:90%
>> SHELDRAKE: Yes.

00:40:36.600 --> 00:40:38.280 align:middle line:90%
Well, that's the thing, you see.

00:40:38.280 --> 00:40:41.810 align:middle line:84%
All religions provide a range
of spiritual practices--

00:40:41.810 --> 00:40:42.690 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Exactly.

00:40:42.690 --> 00:40:45.830 align:middle line:84%
>> SHELDRAKE: --which is
what I've been writing about.

00:40:45.830 --> 00:40:48.360 align:middle line:84%
Meditation is one that's
in all traditions.

00:40:48.360 --> 00:40:52.260 align:middle line:84%
The Christian version
is contemplative prayer.

00:40:52.260 --> 00:40:55.530 align:middle line:84%
But all have singing
and chanting.

00:40:55.530 --> 00:40:58.030 align:middle line:84%
So you sing and chant
with other people.

00:40:58.030 --> 00:41:00.630 align:middle line:84%
And this has scientifically
proven effects

00:41:00.630 --> 00:41:03.870 align:middle line:84%
on making you feel better,
more interconnected,

00:41:03.870 --> 00:41:06.720 align:middle line:90%
lowering stress, and so forth.

00:41:06.720 --> 00:41:10.470 align:middle line:84%
If you just go to church,
you get to sing just

00:41:10.470 --> 00:41:11.370 align:middle line:90%
by going to church.

00:41:11.370 --> 00:41:14.460 align:middle line:90%
It's just part of what you do.

00:41:14.460 --> 00:41:16.350 align:middle line:84%
Then there's the
observation of festivals

00:41:16.350 --> 00:41:19.740 align:middle line:84%
throughout the year, which gives
meaning to life and structure

00:41:19.740 --> 00:41:21.210 align:middle line:90%
to community.

00:41:21.210 --> 00:41:24.240 align:middle line:84%
Then there's the emphasis on
helping other people, which

00:41:24.240 --> 00:41:26.370 align:middle line:90%
all religions encourage.

00:41:26.370 --> 00:41:29.610 align:middle line:84%
It's not just about me
and me getting ahead.

00:41:29.610 --> 00:41:32.190 align:middle line:90%
It's about helping others.

00:41:32.190 --> 00:41:36.630 align:middle line:84%
It's a key part
of all religions.

00:41:36.630 --> 00:41:39.240 align:middle line:84%
And then there's
the, again, going

00:41:39.240 --> 00:41:43.230 align:middle line:84%
