of continuity and tradition

00:41:43.230 --> 00:41:45.610 align:middle line:84%
and the sacrinization
of the Earth.

00:41:45.610 --> 00:41:48.520 align:middle line:84%
In many traditions, including
the Christian tradition,

00:41:48.520 --> 00:41:52.050 align:middle line:84%
