00:42:04.920 --> 00:42:07.360 align:middle line:84%
Other people just
feel, oh, I'm so smart,

00:42:07.360 --> 00:42:08.400 align:middle line:90%
I don't need all that.

00:42:08.400 --> 00:42:09.530 align:middle line:90%
I've seen through it.

00:42:09.530 --> 00:42:10.950 align:middle line:90%
>> REGINA: Right.

00:42:10.950 --> 00:42:12.120 align:middle line:90%
